94%259f%25e6%2585%258b%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%259f%25a5%25e9%2583%25a8%25e9%2596%2580-%25e8%25bc%25bb%25e5%25b0%2584%25e9%2587%258f%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25a2%259e15%25e5%2580%258d&h=ad0426ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200406/s00005/1586166322171/%e5%88%87%e7%88%be%e8%ab%be%e8%b2%9d%e7%88%be%e6%a0%b8%e9%9b%bb%e7%ab%99%e9%99%84%e8%bf%91%e7%8f%be%e5%b1%b1%e7%81%ab-%e7%94%9f%e6%85%8b%e6%aa%a2%e6%9f%a5%e9%83%a8%e9%96%80-%e8%bc%bb%e5%b0%84%e9%87%8f%e5%a4%a7%e5%a2%9e15%e5%80%8d</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuazczU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuazczU.jpg&h=6d64b302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭切爾諾貝爾核電站附近上周六（4日）發生森林大火，生態檢查部門稱火場中心輻射較正常大增15倍。<br />\n<br />\n基輔當局派出兩架飛機、一架直升機和約100名消防員到場滅火。緊急部周日（5日）早上發聲明，稱已看不到有明火，空氣中亦沒發現輻射量上升。不過，該部門前一日曾表示，部分地方因輻射增加而令撲滅大火工作變得困難，同時強調附近居民沒有危險。<br />\n<br />\n不過，生態檢查處長菲爾索夫（Yegor Firsov）周日在facebook發文，<span style=\"color: red;\">上載的片段顯示探測輻射的蓋革計數器（Geiger counter）讀數，是正常數值的16倍</span>。他又說，火場面積約100公頃，較前一天大4倍。<br />\n<br />\n切爾諾貝爾核電站第4號反應堆在1986年發生爆炸，為歐洲帶來廣泛污染，鄰近核電站地區的影響尤為嚴重，民眾被禁在方圓30公里內居住。核電站另外3座反應堆則繼續運作至2000年全面關閉。《衛報》稱，當地森林發生火災並非罕見。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"揸住測計器嗰個記者死咗未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"&quot;There is bad news -- in the center of the fire, radiation is above normal,&quot; Egor Firsov, head of Ukraine's ecological inspection service, wrote in a Facebook post alongside a video of a Geiger counter. &quot;As you can see in the video, the readings of the device are 2.3, when the norm is 0.14. But this is only within the area of the fire outbreak.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nHis measurements refer to the microsievert per hour (&mu;Sv/h) reading; the maximum allowable amount of natural background radiation is 0.5 &mu;Sv/h, the emergency services said, but Firsov's reported amount was nearly five times that.<br />\n<br />\ncopied from cnn<br />\n<br />\n平時0.14依家2.3<br />\n唔逗留太耐應該都冇野掛<